  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Tax Assistant",
  "description": "<p>Descriptions:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>1.  Assist and support in providing tax compliance and advisory services to clients spanning various industries</p>\n<p>2.  Prepare clients' corporate and individual tax returns, including estimated chargeable income filing and withholding tax returns</p>\n<p>3.  Assist clients in responding to queries from the tax authorities</p>\n<p>4.  Attend to queries from clients and all matters arising from a portfolio of clients</p>\n<p>5.  Other tax related tasks</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Degree/ACCA in Accountancy and Tax with 2-5 years experiences</p>\n<p>- Excellent communications skills</p>\n<p>- Systematic, analytical and through approach to work, with a sense of accountability, integrity and discretion</p>\n<p>- Committed to self-development and company's growth</p>\n<p>- Good knowledge of tax laws and regulations</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Other:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- ATTRACTIVE Remuneration/ Salary to commensurate with experience and competence</p>\n<p>- 5 days work week</p>\n<p>- In-house training will be provided</p>",
